bi, features a sliding front vent to adjust ventilation to suit your needs and the weather. The new helmet adorned the heads of several of the Ineos Grenadiers team at last weekend’s Strade Bianche.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>But <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/brand/kask/\">Kask</a> says that it’s designed as a high-end lid to satisfy the needs of a wide range of riders.</span></p><p><span>“We are excited to introduce to our collection a helmet that is truly designed to be worn in all seasons and terrains, and we look forward to watching how its active ventilation and thermoregulating capabilities meet the demands of road cyclists, gravel and cyclocross riders everywhere,” says Diego Zambon, general manager at Kask.&nbsp;</span></p><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=298%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=598%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=898%2C599 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=298%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=598%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=898%2C599 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=354%2C236, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=708%2C472 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=354%2C236, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=708%2C472 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 425px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=403%2C269, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=808%2C539 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 425px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=403%2C269, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=808%2C539 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=553%2C369\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=553%2C369\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=406%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=814%2C543 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=406%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=814%2C543 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Michal Kwiatkowski wearing Kask Wasabi helmet at Strade Bianche\" title=\"Michal Kwiatkowski wearing Kask Wasabi helmet at Strade Bianche\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Michal Kwiatkowski was among the Ineos Grenadiers riders to wear the new helmet at Strade Bianche.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Tim de Waele / Getty Images</i></span></p></div><p><span>Ventilation is adjusted by sliding up and down the middle panel in the shell, opening or closing vents.</span></p><p><span>It’s a similar feature to the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/lazers-second-iteration-of-the-bullet-aero-helmet-is-here/\">Lazer Bullet 2.0 helmet</a>, which also has a central sliding vent that moves up to let air flow through a wide vent at the front of the helmet and via internal channelling to the large vents at the rear.&nbsp;</span></p><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C200, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C400 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1200%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C200, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C400 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1200%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=355%2C236, https://images.immedia