esize=816%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1224%2C815 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=408%2C272, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=816%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1224%2C815 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C741 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C741 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Kask Wasabi helmet\" title=\"Kask Wasabi helmet\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Sliding open the front vent only increases drag by one watt, says Kask.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Kask</i></span></p></div><p><span>Kask says that closing the front vent will increase the temperature of a rider’s head by 1.5ºC.</span></p><p><span>That may not sound a lot, but with less air rushing around your noggin, it’s likely to make a chilly ride much more comfortable. The all-season usability is also helped by Merino wool pads that extend along the inside of the helmet.</span></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-road-bike-helmets/\">Best road bike helmets</a></li></ul><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1199%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1199%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e